data.enText: despite sth that you have just mentioned

data.chText: 我们几乎没有可能改变法律。不过，重要的是我们努力争取。
data.enText: There is little chance that we will succeed in changing the law. Nevertheless, it is important that we try.

data.chText: 我们的失败是意料中的事，尽管如此，还是令人失望。
data.enText: Our defeat was expected but it is disappointing nevertheless.

ex.chText: 无论如何，咱们暂时别再提这事了。
ex.enText: Anyway, let's forget about the matter for the moment.

ex.chText: 天下着雨，不过我们还是去野餐了。
ex.enText: It was raining, but we went to have a picnic anyway.

ex.chText: 路面上结着冰，尽管如此，他还是去上学了。
ex.enText: The road was icy, but he went to school anyhow/anyway.

ex.chText: 她病了，不过还得干家务。
ex.enText: She was sick, but she had to do the housework anyhow/anyway.

ex.chText: 这是一番好的忠告，不过就是不太悦耳。
ex.enText: It was good advice, but it was nevertheless unkind.

ex.chText: 他有点傻气，不过我还是喜欢他的。
ex.enText: He is a bit silly, but I like him nevertheless.

synonyms.bx: 在句中的位置比较灵活。

tr: despite anything to the contrary (usually following a concession)
example: although I'm a little afraid, however I'd like to try it
while we disliked each other, nevertheless we agreed
he was a stern yet fair master
granted that it is dangerous, all the same I still want to go

value.def: You use nevertheless when saying something that contrasts with what has just been said.

example.ex: Most marriages fail after between five and nine years. Nevertheless, people continue to get married.
example.tran: 大部分婚姻在婚后第五至第九年间失败，然而，人们仍会选择结婚。

example.ex: There had been no indication of any loss of mental faculties. His whole life had nevertheless been clouded with a series of illnesses.
example.tran: 没有迹象显示他的智力受到了损害，但是他的一生却是疾病缠身。
